OL,3,C'He butchered my son': Man found
OL,4,Cguilty of Damien Heagney killing
OL,6,FA man accused of murdering,
OL,7,Fdismembering and then dumping the
OL,8,Fremains of Damien Heagney has been
OL,9,Ffound guilty.
OL,11,FStephen McCourt, 41, of Riverview in
OL,12,FAugher claimed he had nothing to do
OL,13,Fwith Mr Heagney's death but the jury
OL,14,Fof 3 women and 8 men did not believe
OL,15,Fhim.
OL,17,FThe Judge told McCourt that he had
OL,18,Fbeen found guilty of murder and that
OL,19,Fthere is only one sentence he could
OL,20,Fimpose, which was a life sentence.
