OL,3,C'He butchered my son': Man found
OL,4,Cguilty of Damien Heagney killing
OL,6,FAs the verdict was given, Mr Heagney's
OL,7,Fmother was crying and extremely upset.
OL,8,FShe said: "He butchered my son."
OL,10,FMcCourt will find out how long he will
OL,11,Fspend in prison next month.
OL,13,FMr Heagney was last seen alive at the
OL,14,Fend of December 2021. He was reported
OL,15,Fmissing in July 2022 and on 10 August
OL,16,F2022, his dismembered remains were
OL,17,Ffound at Cappagh reservoir in Co
OL,18,FTyrone.
